HLPSCORE {
[1;36mTopic: Scoring

Scores are based upon the size of your empire and the number and class of kills
you have accumulated in ship-to-ship combat.  Each class of ship is worth a
different number of points.

Cybertron Scouts are worth 1000 points. More powerful Cybertrons are worth
more; you will have to destroy them to find how much.

